\f2\b0\fs21 \cf16 \cb31 \strokec16 Manato gains extra Sheer Force based on his Max HP, with every 1 point of Max HP increasing Sheer Force by 0.1.\cb1 \
\cb31 All 
\f0\b \cf26 \strokec26 Fire DMG
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  Manato deals is Sheer DMG, ignoring enemy DEF and using his Sheer Force stat as the DMG Multiplier.\cb1 \
\cb31 When Manato uses 
\f0\b \cf30 \strokec30 Special Attack: Return to Ashes - Sacrifice
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  or a 
\f0\b \cf30 \strokec30 Defensive Assist
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 , he accumulates 
\f0\b \cf30 \strokec30 Blazing Heart
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 , up to a maximum of 100 points. At 75 
\f0\b \cf30 \strokec30 Blazing Heart
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 , Manato enters the 
\f0\b \cf30 \strokec30 Molten Edge
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  state. While in the 
\f0\b \cf30 \strokec30 Molten Edge
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  state, Manato consumes 3.3 
\f0\b \cf30 \strokec30 Blazing Heart
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  per second. When 
\f0\b \cf30 \strokec30 Blazing Heart
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  is fully depleted, he exits 
\f0\b \cf30 \strokec30 Molten Edge
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 .\cb1 \
\cb31 While in the 
\f0\b \cf30 \strokec30 Molten Edge
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  state, Manato's 
\f0\b \cf30 \strokec30 Basic Attacks
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  are enhanced, and he can use 
\f0\b \cf30 \strokec30 EX Special Attack: Return to Ashes - Fall
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 .\cb1 \
\cb31 When consuming HP during 
\f0\b \cf30 \strokec30 Basic Attack: Blazing Wind - Misty Slash
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  or during the consecutive slashes from an 
\f0\b \cf30 \strokec30 Assist Follow-Up
